entry.title: The Gaza Strip: What to Know, Maps and History

entry.title: Barred From Office by Maduro, This Venezuelan Politician Thinks She Can Still Beat Him
entry.content: Opposition politician María Corina Machado wants to challenge the country’s authoritarian president, Nicolás Maduro, at the ballot box. The effort may be hopeless.
